Released October 2025 in the US, Monster Bad Apple is a can I feel like I've
seen before but actually never have. I may've seen images of it online, as
the UK market got it more than a year before the US. The art on the front of
this can is pretty cool and features a girl with dirty blonde hair and red eyes
holding up an apple. She's meant to be the first woman created by God, Eve, not
some random person.

