I guess when you look at the can closer it seems the girl isn't wearing any
clothing, or at least none that's visible, so the guess of her being Eve checks
out. Hell yes, more odd religious references on energy drinks please. [Bottoms
up. And the Devil laughs.](https://youtu.be/bntfUA6TmLs?t=103) Something to
think about.

