It's carbonated apple juice. There is no further insight I can provide; that's
it. It's not unbearably sweet and the carbonation is light. Like other Monster
juices it's very easy to drink and refreshing. At 170 calories it's lighter than
other sugary Monsters of similar size, but not much. It still sits heavy on the
stomach. Surprisingly, it's only 6% juice by volume.

